title: Kim Kardashian posts “porn” throwback photo from W magazine shoot |
text:
The 34-year-old shared a snap on Instagram of her 2010 W magazine photo shoot — where the pregnant star stripped naked and rolled around in silver paint.
“#TBT shooting my @wmag cover,” she captioned the photo of herself lying naked in a pool of silver body paint.
While she seems to be proud of the pics now, that wasn’t always the case.
W magazine shoot (Frame content direct link: https://instagram.com/p/5N-galuS8v/embed .)
In 2011, an episode of Kourtney and Kim Take New York showed Mrs. Kardashian West distraught with the magazine once it hit newsstands.
“I’m so f**king mad right now!” she cried.
“[They] promised me I would be covered in artwork on top of me. It was so uncomfortable. I’m really honestly freaking out.”
“It really pisses me off, this is serious porn. They weren’t going to show my ass crack or my nipples. This is full f**king porn.”
Then she got momager Kris on the phone.
“Mom, have you seen my cover? I feel so f**king taken advantage of!” she bawled.
“They promised me I’d be fully covered. Did you see the inside? I just am never getting naked again.”
Well, never say never, Kim ...
Kim on the cover of Paper Magazine. Source: Supplied
